for select 

<option ng-repeat="x in names">{{x}}</option>  or   <select ng-model="selectedName" ng-options="x for x in names"></select> 

<select ng-model="selectedCar" ng-options="x for (x, y) in cars"></select>

data source, x represents the key, and y represents the value 
car01 : {brand : "Ford", model : "Mustang", color : "red"},
selectedCar={brand : "Ford", model : "Mustang", color : "red"}.



